@startuml
skinparam sequence {
ArrowColor black
LifeLineBorderColor black
LifeLineBackgroundColor khaki
ParticipantBackgroundColor lightgoldenrodyellow
}
Actor User
participant Front
participant Ads
participant Promotion

User -> Front: 进入打车首页

activate Front
    Front -> Ads: 请求广告位-半页卡（广告类型-63）
        activate Ads
        Ads -> Ads: 城市、周期、生效时段、渠道、\n频次、人群、实验等过滤
        Ads -> Promotion: 渠道活动组领券
            activate Promotion
                Promotion --> Ads : 领券结果
            deactivate Promotion
        alt 没领到券
            Ads -> Ads: 过滤该广告
        end
        Ads -> Ads: 数据封装及排序、优先级排序
        Ads -> Front: 广告数据返回
        deactivate Ads
Front -> User: 展示广告
deactivate Front

@enduml